# Title: Tor Client/Browser Execution
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-02-20
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the use of Tor or Tor-Browser to connect to onion routing networks
# MITRE Tactic: Command and Control
# Tags: attack.command-and-control, attack.t1090.003
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_browsers_tor_execution.yml

Description="Tor Browser" OR Product="Tor Browser" OR Image IN ("*\\tor.exe", "*\\Tor Browser\\Browser\\firefox.exe")